<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="so">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Website Qurux Badan</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    nav {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 15px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 15px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #ffeb3b;
    }

    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      animation: slideUp 1.5s ease;
    }

    section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    section p {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    footer {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {opacity: 0;}
      to {opacity: 1;}
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
      from {transform: translateY(50px); opacity: 0;}
      to {transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Ku Soo Dhawoow Website Qurux Badan</h1>
    <p>Halkaan waxaad ka heli doontaa naqshad casri ah oo dadka ku yaabiya!</p>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="#">Bogga Hore</a>
    <a href="#">Adeegyada</a>
    <a href="#">Nagu Saabsan</a>
    <a href="#">La Xiriir</a>
  </nav>

  <section>
    <h2>Naqshad Casri ah</h2>
    <p>Website-kan waxaa loogu talagalay in uu dadka ku qanciyo oo ku tuso naqshad qurux badan oo casri ah. Midabada gradient-ka, animation-ka iyo qaabka nadiifka ah ayaa ka dhigaya mid soo jiidasho leh.</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2026 mohamett bashiir. Xuquuqda way dhamaan.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
